                     <interp inst="t18340410-49-person426" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer of the City. I received charge of the prisoner, and produce the property.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was in great distress, and in a state of starvation. I had no employment for half a year.</p>
